# LyRT

### Installation

* Requirements:
  * python3
  * python3-pip

* Installing on Ubuntu 16.04

```
$ sudo apt install python3 python3-pip python3-venv
$ python3 -m venv myvenv
$ source myvenv/bin/activate
(myvenv)$
```

